---
// UseCasesBenefits.astro – Use cases and benefits for agencies and individual bloggers
---
<section id="benefits" class="container mx-auto min-h-[40vh] py-20 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-8 snap-start">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 items-center text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white">Who Is It For?</h2>
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Designed to empower both content agencies and solo creators. Save time, boost SEO, and keep your editorial calendar on track.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 w-full mt-6">
    <!-- Content Agencies -->
    <div class="flex flex-col p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-800/20 via-orange-600/10 to-slate-900/20 border border-orange-500/10 shadow-lg">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">For Content Agencies</h3>
      <ul class="text-gray-300 text-base space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Scale content production for multiple clients without sacrificing quality</li>
        <li>Configure unique AI agents for each brand, tone, or campaign</li>
        <li>Collaborate in real-time; manage drafts, reviews, and exports for teams</li>
        <li>Automate SEO optimization for every article</li>
        <li>Streamline client approvals and export in preferred formats</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <!-- Individual Bloggers -->
    <div class="flex flex-col p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-800/20 via-blue-600/10 to-slate-900/20 border border-blue-400/10 shadow-lg">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">For Individual Bloggers</h3>
      <ul class="text-gray-300 text-base space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Never run out of ideas—AI agents help you generate new post topics and outlines</li>
        <li>Get a draft ready in minutes, not hours</li>
        <li>Maintain a consistent publishing schedule with automated reminders</li>
        <li>Ensure every post is SEO-optimized for maximum reach</li>
        <li>Export content directly to Markdown, HTML, or DOCX</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

